Share this on WhatsAppSpread the loveGrammy-winning singer, Burna Boy, has announced his next album and it’s named after himself, Love Damini.
Sharing on Twitter, the artiste, who sold out the Madison Square Garden in New York on Thursday said, “Love, Damini is a personal body of work. It’s about the ups and downs, the growth, the L’s and W’s. I’m excited to share this journey and roll out with you all #LoveDamini #Burnaboy.”
He had on Wednesday hinted that it will be dropping this year.
